{"type":"message","id":"41f52931","parentId":"7b2c482d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T00:43:41.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到文件被损坏了，有 BOM 和编码问题。让我用 write 工具重新创建整个文件，包含之前的所有内容和新的第 15 次思考。我需要从之前的读取中恢复内容。\n\n实际上，让我先用 exec 命令把文件恢复到第 14 次思考结束时的状态，然后再正确追加第 15 次。\n\n让我先读取文件找到第 14 次思考结束的位置，然后截断文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_50aacdf975bf4a99a7118e1a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 读取文件并找到第 14 次思考的结尾，然后截断损坏的部分\n$content = Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\人体进化思考日志.md\" -Raw -Encoding UTF8\n# 找到最后一个完整的 \"---\" 在第 14 次思考后\n$pattern = \"(?s)(.*## 人体进化思考 - 第 14 次.*?老年衰弱.*?可逆转的状态\\.\\n\\n---\\n)\"\n$match = [regex]::Match($content, $pattern)\nif ($match.Success) {\n    $cleanContent = $match.Groups[1].Value\n    $utf8NoBom = New-Object System.Text.UTF8Encoding $false\n    [System.IO.File]::WriteAllText(\"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\人体进化思考日志.md\", $cleanContent, $utf8NoBom)\n    Write-Host \"文件已恢复到第 14 次思考结束\"\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"未找到匹配模式\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774313007306}}
